
## Kruskal-Wallis Rank Sum Test

```{r GetRStatix}
library(rstatix)
```

```{r DataName.kt}
DataName.kt = DataName %>% kruskal_test(ResponseName ~ FactorName)
DataName.kt %>% kable()
```


```{r DunnTest}
DataName.dt = DataName %>% dunn_test((ResponseName ~ FactorName)
DataName.dt %>% kable()
```

```{r getMeans}
get_emmeans(DataName.dt)DataName.kt %>% kable()
```
